title: FEAR THE WALKING DEAD S1 [400p.XVID.MP3] MINIMIZE THE SUCK EDIT
description:
I had a theory that the problem with "Fear The Walking Dead" was that the producers took two or three decent episodes and tortuously stretched them out to fill six episodes.

I think I was right.

After editing out OVER TWO HOURS of bloated, useless garbage, what I ending up with was an okay "Walking Dead" spin off.
